\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f1\fs18\b0\i0\super\cf1 12\~}{\f1\fs18\b0\i0\cf1 The accommodations would have disadvantaged respondent to some extent, but since he suggested both options I do not consider whether an employer would satisfy his duty to accommodate by offering these choices to an unwilling employee.  Cf.   (employer does not discharge his duty to accommodate by offering to transfer an electrician to an unskilled position).  }}]]></Comment>
